#### Description

This dashboard provides visibility into vulnerabilities within the Nozomi Networks platform using the Node CVE data stream.

It shows total, resolved, and unresolved CVEs, with trends over time. Vulnerabilities are categorized by type and CWE, and high-severity CVEs are highlighted. A saved search displays key CVE details to support risk assessment and remediation.

**[Integration Page](/app/integrations/detail/nozomi_networks/overview)**
